      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey... im kinda freaked out. i keep having this exact same dream every single night lately. it’s not even a normal dream, it’s like... i'm just walking down a street and there's this huge neon sign for a specific brand of energy drink, \"Volt-Rush\" or something. it's so vivid and it feels less like a dream and more like someone is forcing the image into my head. has anyone else ever talked about this happening?",
